Norman: Why'd you even reel this sucker up, man? What are you gonna do with a catfish? #portrait:norman
Sam: Dunno, the kids sometimes think they look cool... I like to show them all the different fish we can catch. #portrait:sam
Norman: That's respectable, I suppose. You ever try to catch the sharks out here? #portrait:norman
Sam: If I had a boat, maybe, but I'm kind of saving up for a house first. Living with the parents is getting troublesome. #portrait:sam
Norman: Ah, I remember when I first moved out. It was scary for a while. You don't realize how many things they take care of until you can't rely on it anymore. #portrait:norman
Sam: I figure it'll be tough, but hey, gotta make the leap sometime. #portrait:sam

